students who knew young Asselin.</i>

41:14.549 --> 41:15.842
Where's your man!

41:16.217 --> 41:17.343
The little neighbour was fun,

41:17.468 --> 41:18.970
I just wanted to play with her.

41:19.095 --> 41:22.140
- We were still in Laval, then--
- It's my story!

41:22.265 --> 41:25.184
Hun, you gotta give context,
put some meat around the bone!

41:25.309 --> 41:26.686
