41:35.611 --> 41:38.656
But I don't know a goddamn--

41:38.781 --> 41:40.992
Quit swearing! Goddamn, goddamn...

41:41.492 --> 41:44.370
Not a fucking word of English.
But when Mom and Dad

41:44.495 --> 41:46.414
