what they were saying,

41:46.539 --> 41:47.582
they'd speak English.

41:48.082 --> 41:51.377
It'd always end with,
"Shut up! Fuck off!"

41:51.502 --> 41:53.504
So I'd tell Barbara
across the street,

41:53.629 --> 41:56.549
