48:08.671 --> 48:12.007
Not a dull moment with Steve.

48:18.514 --> 48:20.266
There you have it.

48:20.391 --> 48:22.143
Fasten your seatbelt.

48:26.772 --> 48:27.982
Gawd help us all...

48:46.959 --> 48:48.002
