1:47:24.515 --> 1:47:25.975
D'you understand?

1:47:36.652 --> 1:47:38.696
D'ya pack your bags like I asked?

1:47:44.243 --> 1:47:46.203
D'you pack your shit or what?

1:47:51.500 --> 1:47:52.626
Don't tickle me!

1:47:56.964 --> 1:47:58.632
Don't forget the sandwiches!

1:47:59.800 --> 1:48:01.343
Look what I found in the fridge!

1:48:02.094 --> 1:48:03.012
Look!

1:48:03.721 --> 1:48:05.556
How the fuck is that my problem?

1:48:06.932 --> 1:48:08.517
Back door locked, eh?

1:48:15.899 --> 1:48:17.901
It's gonna be an effin trip!

1:48:18.027 --> 1:48:19.820
Do you want this with you, Die?

1:48:19.945 --> 1:48:21.238
Yeah, not in the trunk.

1:48:27.286 --> 1:48:28.829
We got everything?

1:48:29.163 --> 1:48:37.163
Didn't forget anything?

1:53:27.085 --> 1:53:28.086
It's green.

1:53:29.421 --> 1:53:30.339
You okay?

1:53:47.230 --> 1:53:48.857
I gotta use the washroom.

1:53:56.823 --> 1:53:58.033
Let's try this place.

1:55:18.029 --> 1:55:20.031
Mom's pissing?

1:55:43.013 --> 1:55:44.598
Am I squishing you?

1:56:59.089 --> 1:57:01.174
You motherfucking bitch from hell!

1:57:01.967 --> 1:57:03.718
Take it easy! Take it easy!

1:57:04.094 --> 1:57:05.679
Back off, asshole!

1:57:06.346 --> 1:57:08.848
Don't touch me, don't talk to me!
- Chill out, bro!

1:57:21.027 --> 1:57:22.988
- Easy, easy, easy...
- Relax, we're here to help.

1:57:24.739 --> 1:57:26.866
Why you doing this to me,
you bitch!

1:57:26.992 --> 1:57:29.828
It's for you own good, sweetie!

1:57:30.412 --> 1:57:32.372
My own good, you fucking traitor!

1:57:33.206 --> 1:57:35.542
You dump me here like goddamn trash!

1:57:35.667 --> 1:57:37.961
You got sick of me!
You're done with me!

1:57:44.217 --> 1:57:46.386
Don't be violent, Steve.
There's no point.

1:57:46.511 --> 1:57:49.055
Shut up!
You gonna taze my ass, bitch!

1:57:49.180 --> 1:57:51.474
You want 'em
to fucking electrocute me!

1:57:56.855 --> 1:58:00.233
I won't touch you if you come
in the hospital without resisting.

1:58:00.942 --> 1:58:02.569
No! I ain't mad!

1:58:02.694 --> 1:58:04.821
I ain't goin in a hospital!
Do I look fucking crazy?

1:58:04.946 --> 1:58:06.197
No one here's crazy, pal.

1:58:06.531 --> 1:58:10.035
Stop it! No! I won't go! Mom!

1:58:10.785 --> 1:58:12.662
I don't wanna go! I won't!

1:58:14.122 --> 1:58:16.791
Don't leave me here!
Don't do this to me!

1:58:18.835 --> 1:58:19.753
Mom!

1:58:23.089 --> 1:58:26.134
And you, you fucking wimp!
You too?

1:58:26.509 --> 1:58:28.970
You bitches are all against me!
All of you!

1:58:29.095 --> 1:58:30.513
I said back the fuck off!

1:58:32.307 --> 1:58:33.808
Is that fucking necessary!

1:58:33.933 --> 1:58:36.311
Let us do our job!

1:58:36.436 --> 1:58:38.647
- Drop that!
- You gonna fucking hurt me!

1:58:39.606 --> 1:58:40.940
Calm the fuck down, man!

1:58:41.066 --> 1:58:41.900
Calm down!

1:58:43.735 --> 1:58:44.653
Let me fucking go!

1:58:44.778 --> 1:58:45.779
Let him go!

1:58:47.280 --> 1:58:48.573
Son of a bitch!

1:58:51.201 --> 1:58:52.327
Let go of him!

1:58:53.328 --> 1:58:54.454
Son of a bitch!

1:58:54.579 --> 1:58:56.039
I'm just doing my job, ma'am!

1:58:56.164 --> 1:58:58.667
He hit my son!

1:58:59.000 --> 1:59:02.045
He hit him! He hit him!

1:59:02.170 --> 1:59:04.297
You signed the form!

1:59:04.422 --> 1:59:06.091
Let us do our job!
That's enough, ma'am!

1:59:06.216 --> 1:59:08.468
I didn't sign for you
to hit my son!

1:59:08.593 --> 1:59:10.178
Withdrawal clause ends
in 24 hours!

1:59:10.303 --> 1:59:11.805
Fuck your clause!

1:59:12.138 --> 1:59:15.141
- Come back in 24 hours, ma'am!
- Mom, he's hurting me!

1:59:15.475 --> 1:59:17.727
I'm his mother, I decide!

1:59:17.852 --> 1:59:18.812
Not anymore!

1:59:22.524 --> 1:59:25.318
What are they doing to him?
I changed my mind!

1:59:25.443 --> 1:59:27.028
Get out of the fucking way!

1:59:28.029 --> 1:59:36.029
Son of a bitch!

2:01:39.619 --> 2:01:41.663
There goes the forest...

2:01:42.831 --> 2:01:45.083
Forest again...

2:01:47.418 --> 2:01:49.462
And, now the beach, okay...

2:02:25.206 --> 2:02:27.792
<i>Hi, you've reached Diane's voice-mail.</i>

2:02:27.917 --> 2:02:28.918
<i>Leave a message</i>

2:02:29.794 --> 2:02:31.212
<i>and I'll call you back
as soon as possible.</i>

2:02:31.754 --> 2:02:33.172
<i>Thank you, bye, have a nice day.</i>

2:02:34.465 --> 2:02:36.092
Hey, it's me.

2:02:36.759 --> 2:02:39.512
I bet you must be
cleaning up your houses...

2:02:40.722 --> 2:02:42.932
I'm pretty bad-ass high...

2:02:44.309 --> 2:02:46.394
I was calling to say...

2:02:51.065 --> 2:02:53.234
Yo Die,
I'm so fucking ripped, serious...

2:02:54.903 --> 2:02:56.738
If you could see my face...

2:02:57.155 --> 2:02:59.532
You'd laugh your ass off!

2:03:02.076 --> 2:03:04.120
I thought you were gonna answer.

2:03:04.704 --> 2:03:06.205
I wanted to tell you...

2:03:10.501 --> 2:03:12.462
I just wanted to...

2:03:12.587 --> 2:03:14.964
thank you for your patience.

2:03:16.215 --> 2:03:19.177
I know I'm rough.

2:03:19.302 --> 2:03:21.471
Like Grandma used to say
when I was younger,

2:03:21.596 --> 2:03:22.722
that I was rough.

2:03:23.389 --> 2:03:25.767
Now I get it, why she said that.

2:03:26.976 --> 2:03:28.561
So... I'm sorry.

2:03:30.188 --> 2:03:31.397
And...

2:03:36.110 --> 2:03:37.153
And when...

2:03:38.112 --> 2:03:40.281
When I think about the times when...

2:03:42.742 --> 2:03:45.787
When I think about
how much maybe I hurt you...

2:03:47.538 --> 2:03:51.042
After, when I get my shit together...

2:03:53.920 --> 2:03:55.880
I'm so fucking sad because...

2:03:56.005 --> 2:03:58.758
you deserve so much better
than a fucking retard like me!

2:04:03.930 --> 2:04:04.973
So...

2:04:09.352 --> 2:04:13.731
What matters is... I'm thinking
about you here, and I love you.

2:04:17.902 --> 2:04:21.447
Tell Kyla I said hi.

2:04:29.163 --> 2:04:30.999
Was it okay?

2:04:35.378 --> 2:04:37.213
I mean, was it...

2:04:38.047 --> 2:04:39.799
I was okay? 'Ight.

2:04:46.556 --> 2:04:47.890
I rang.

2:04:48.641 --> 2:04:50.810
I didn't hear ya,
it must be broken.

2:04:54.397 --> 2:04:57.775
I'm cleaning up that shed,
it's a freakin' pigsty.

2:05:00.570 --> 2:05:01.946
Are you okay?

2:05:02.280 --> 2:05:03.865
Of course!

2:05:03.990 --> 2:05:06.451
You?
Long time no see, stranger!

2:05:07.493 --> 2:05:10.038
You wanna come in, have a beer?

2:05:10.163 --> 2:05:13.124
Watch some TV,
I finally plugged it in.

2:05:13.249 --> 2:05:14.709
It's just about time I did.

2:05:16.419 --> 2:05:17.378
Have a beer!

2:05:18.129 --> 2:05:21.591
We can have dinner too,
I'll fix some pasta...

2:05:22.592 --> 2:05:23.634
Come on!

2:05:24.802 --> 2:05:25.887
There!

2:05:28.056 --> 2:05:29.307
My good glasses...

2:05:43.613 --> 2:05:47.658
I came to tell you
we're moving to Toronto.

2:05:48.326 --> 2:05:49.744
For Patrick's job.

2:05:55.458 --> 2:05:57.001
Get outta here!

2:05:57.752 --> 2:06:00.379
Well, that ain't dull news, Toronto!

2:06:01.130 --> 2:06:02.381
Jeez, I only got beer!

2:06:03.049 --> 2:06:06.052
Had I known, I would have gotten
something more fancy! To party!

2:06:06.844 --> 2:06:08.596
I'll be damned!

2:06:09.430 --> 2:06:11.557
I lived in Toronto, once!

2:06:12.016 --> 2:06:13.810
Ages ago, though, but...

2:06:15.019 --> 2:06:17.438
Just before Steve, actually.

2:06:17.563 --> 2:06:21.609
I'd written down tons of addresses
and places and...

2:06:21.734 --> 2:06:25.947
in that huge, huge address book
I could give you...

2:06:26.739 --> 2:06:28.574
'Cause you can't tell right away,

2:06:29.742 --> 2:06:32.912
but Toronto can be an effin bore
if you dunno your way around.

2:06:33.579 --> 2:06:35.123
All of these places
I spotted, jeez...

2:06:35.456 --> 2:06:39.502
Restaurants, some good ones,
and cute shops, not tourist-traps.

2:06:40.378 --> 2:06:42.964
There's no way I threw that away!
Where the hell is it...

2:06:43.881 --> 2:06:45.424
When are you guys leaving?

2:06:45.967 --> 2:06:48.469
Well, two months from now,
originally,

2:06:50.304 --> 2:06:51.764
but then...

2:06:53.224 --> 2:06:57.270
they moved it
to two week-ends from now.

2:06:59.272 --> 2:07:00.815
But now...

2:07:00.940 --> 2:07:02.441
finally...

2:07:04.694 --> 2:07:07.446
we're leaving next weekend.

2:07:07.572 --> 2:07:09.198
Shit on a brick!

2:07:09.782 --> 2:07:11.033
Next weekend?!

2:07:11.659 --> 2:07:13.411
Wow!

2:07:17.498 --> 2:07:20.877
Talk about a big project!
Well, that's quite the adventure!

2:07:21.002 --> 2:07:23.963
You're moving to Toronto
next weekend!

2:07:25.339 --> 2:07:27.175
You must be over the effin moon!

2:07:33.347 --> 2:07:35.808
I didn't think you'd react that way.

2:07:39.145 --> 2:07:41.981
What the hell did ya expect!
It's such great news!

2:07:43.608 --> 2:07:46.527
It's awesome!
It's freaking awesome!

2:07:46.652 --> 2:07:47.778
You best write me, girl!

2:07:49.155 --> 2:07:52.200
If you don't, I'll visit you,
I swear I will, want it or not!

2:07:55.369 --> 2:07:57.663
I gotta go back to my boxes...

2:07:58.206 --> 2:08:00.458
Stay, grab a beer!

2:08:00.583 --> 2:08:02.585
Let's have dinner to celebrate!

2:08:02.710 --> 2:08:05.546
By the way,
bugs are eating up my apples,

2:08:05.671 --> 2:08:08.841
I gotta do something with them.
I could bake a pie.

2:08:08.966 --> 2:08:12.762
We'll have some pie. I got some
nice ice cream to put on top!

2:08:15.181 --> 2:08:17.600
I could come back later!

2:08:17.725 --> 2:08:20.061
Come with Patrick!

2:08:20.186 --> 2:08:21.145
And your daughter!

2:08:21.812 --> 2:08:22.730
They never came over!

2:08:37.453 --> 2:08:39.163
I don't want you to think

2:08:39.288 --> 2:08:42.333
these past few months
didn't mean anything to me,

2:08:43.251 --> 2:08:44.627
with you...

2:08:45.795 --> 2:08:47.004
Me too.

2:08:47.630 --> 2:08:49.966
They were important for me too!

2:08:50.091 --> 2:08:51.259
We had fun!

2:08:52.093 --> 2:08:54.637
A shitload of fun!

2:08:55.596 --> 2:08:58.307
You did us good, we loved having ya!

2:08:58.891 --> 2:09:00.101
In my life...

2:09:00.685 --> 2:09:02.603
You more of a pie girl
or crisp girl?

2:09:20.788 --> 2:09:22.915
I can't just abandon...

2:09:27.253 --> 2:09:28.504
...abandon my family...

2:09:41.851 --> 2:09:43.519
That's not what I meant.

2:10:00.494 --> 2:10:01.662
You know, Kyla...

2:10:05.082 --> 2:10:06.751
There's just so many ways to deal.

2:10:08.461 --> 2:10:11.130
You deal with your life,
I deal with mine. That's it.

2:10:18.095 --> 2:10:19.638
I sent him there...

2:10:23.726 --> 2:10:25.227
because I have hope.

2:10:27.188 --> 2:10:29.398
I'm full of hope, okay?

2:10:35.738 --> 2:10:37.865
This world ain't got tons of hope.

2:10:39.492 --> 2:10:41.035
But I like to think...

2:10:43.204 --> 2:10:46.832
that it's full of hopeful people,
hoping all day long.

2:10:50.336 --> 2:10:53.631
Better off that way 'cause us
hopeful people can change things.

2:10:54.632 --> 2:10:56.717
Hopeful world with hopeless people...

2:10:56.842 --> 2:10:59.095
That won't get us far.

2:11:01.430 --> 2:11:02.848
I did what I did...

2:11:07.561 --> 2:11:09.814
so that way, there is hope.

2:11:17.780 --> 2:11:18.989
So I win.

2:11:22.701 --> 2:11:23.953
All the way.

2:11:26.288 --> 2:11:29.625
It's a win-win.
For everybody.

2:11:34.171 --> 2:11:35.339
So...

2:11:36.215 --> 2:11:44.215
pie or crisp?

2:13:23.364 --> 2:13:26.575
Dr. Fawcett will pass by later,
for his meds' eval.

2:13:26.909 --> 2:13:28.827
Hopefully, we can relocate him--

2:13:28.953 --> 2:13:30.704
Nah, Micheline's off tonight.

2:13:31.372 --> 2:13:33.457
She left for St-Paul's
but she's back tonight.

2:13:33.582 --> 2:13:35.834
It's her Thursday.
- She's done with Thursdays.

2:13:36.252 --> 2:13:38.712
Not anymore.
Don't ask.

2:13:39.713 --> 2:13:41.215
Don't try to understand, bro.

2:13:42.633 --> 2:13:44.093
What can you do?

2:13:44.760 --> 2:13:45.886
She's happy with him.

2:13:46.679 --> 2:13:49.640
He started drinking again...
She's back with him, what can I say?

2:13:49.765 --> 2:13:51.892
Is she dumb,
she'll never understand?

2:13:52.017 --> 2:13:53.352
There's nothing to understand.

2:13:53.477 --> 2:13:55.229
She wants to save him.

2:13:55.854 --> 2:14:03.854
Fucking human nature, bro.
